{"tid":433230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［親中遠美］特朗普明訪英被降格為工作訪問，不獲英女皇接見","createTime":"2017-10-12T08:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T11:00:13.000Z","uid":41351,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5bb19ede61b6042e19548420dafdc02680524b7b","tid":433230,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T08:11:59.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普預計明年初訪問英國。英國傳媒報道，外交人員正研究將特朗普的訪問級別，由國事訪問降級至工作訪問，行程亦可能不會會見英女王，稍後才進行最高規格的國事訪問。<br />\n<br />\n報道表示，特朗普可能不會有特別行程來突顯兩國的關係，而是在訪問多國期間，順道訪問英國，以減低爭議性。<br />\n<br />\n英國外交部表示，邀請特朗普國事訪問的立場沒有改變。美國駐英大使館就表示，特朗普目前沒有工作訪問的計劃。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1358693-20171012.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1358693-20171012.htm&d=zxSEwzIAsp08fc7Qcb1rKdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=1a349464\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1358693-20171012.htm&h=eabebfdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1358693-20171012.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/161101_ad5fa8665f5bf4173826a3a7da1d296c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F161101_ad5fa8665f5bf4173826a3a7da1d296c.jpg&h=3e55644b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/161153_cfc6f90f55624b37ec775ba2082a3200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F161153_cfc6f90f55624b37ec775ba2082a3200.jpg&h=fcd1c47a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普上任後，對七個以穆斯林為主的國家，實施入境禁令，引發強烈批評，英國有大批民眾反對特朗普訪英。"},{"pid":"773bfde7e3e56ffd4df8f3f92ea87d07ca361260","tid":433230,"uid":98163,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T08:14:49.000Z","msg":"啲歐洲人一般都覺得美國人又蠢又癡肥"},{"pid":"3f8b3e096bd60934046cb2604bea2a2300181679","tid":433230,"uid":47112,"like":1,"d